Description: Animated 3D VRM characters with AI-powered conversational chat
 Desktop Waifu is an animated 3D desktop companion featuring VRM characters
 with AI-powered conversational abilities. It runs as a Wayland layer shell
 overlay, providing a persistent desktop pet experience.
 .
 Features:
  - 3D VRM character rendering with animations
  - AI-powered chat with multiple LLM providers
  - Wayland overlay mode for seamless desktop integration
  - Customizable characters and personalities
